{"tid":2195724,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解美洲杯咁鐘意邀請亞洲隊參加?","createTime":"2020-09-09T11:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T07:22:13.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"a8b59d805e4fcaff431c8199c01e0e66bda80fd9","tid":2195724,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"而2020年由阿根廷和哥倫比亞聯合舉辦的美洲杯也已經進入了最後準備階段。<br />\n<br />\n屆時，將會有兩支其他大洲的受邀球隊。目前可以確定的是參加今年這屆屆美洲杯的卡塔爾來年還會參加。<br />\n而另一支受邀參加2020美洲杯的球隊是中國隊，不過中國隊回絕了邀請。<br />\n<br />\n對於2019年美洲杯，除了卡塔爾之外，同時參與巴西美洲杯的還有中國的鄰國日本。前不久，日本也公布了美洲杯的大名單，其中有15位都是1997年的適齡國奧球員，而這次選取這批小將，就是在明年東京奧運會做準備。<br />\n<br />\n近2年搵卡塔爾,日本U23,中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2248b34e499aff79baa09fa452ad20d2f30f1bd","tid":2195724,"uid":173952,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:03:43.000Z","msg":"補充最新一屆搵左澳洲代替中國"},{"pid":"6de1d9e15d2c11cdf55d140a9ccc6183ac7d60e7","tid":2195724,"uid":350194,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:04:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母中國唔撚柒去 死撚咗去啦 有嘅話買撚爆大波"},{"pid":"01d1be3b614f6709d5f88a66d7dd259733644fb5","tid":2195724,"uid":132262,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"6de1d9e15d2c11cdf55d140a9ccc6183ac7d60e7","tid":2195724,"uid":350194,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:04:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母中國唔撚柒去 死撚咗去啦 有嘅話買撚爆大波"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:05:51.000Z","msg":"邊夠膽去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />三零部隊"},{"pid":"1e2dd290ac36aa28a57b78099a3e777a4baa5b7e","tid":2195724,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:07:17.000Z","msg":"想亞洲人感受到球王風采"},{"pid":"d3396cd4e81a8d98644880a9a32c2a10a490d758","tid":2195724,"uid":5367